headline: If You'd Bought 1 Share of Costco Wholesale at Its IPO, Here's How Many Shares You Would Own Now
summary: Costco Wholesale (NASDAQ: COST) can be a fun place to shop.  Following solid financial results this year, the stock price recently hit a new all-time high of $1,008.  Costco went public at $10 per share.
